Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:02.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.57,0:00:04.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time for Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.14,0:00:06.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gather all the shards\nof the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:08.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'll destroy Naraku\nwith my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:10.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}While Inuyasha fights,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Band of Seven attack the temple{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:14.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Miroku, Sango and Kagome\nstop breathing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:18.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... I tried to do my best!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.15,0:00:20.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku, Sango, Shippo and Kirara...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.82,0:00:21.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}travel back in time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:22.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To a Feudal Fairy Tale{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:24.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:06.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure is impure\nlmpure is pure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:11.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Seven-Man Mound is where\nthe bodies of seven mercenaries
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:13.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,known as the Band of Seven\nwere buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:16.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Recently, it split into two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:19.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:23.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The bones of the seven mercenaries\nburied here all disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:27.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're so worried that it's\nsome kind of curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:32.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall purify the site.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:37.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you so much,\NPriestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:40.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- What a relief!\N- That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:43.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll put their minds\nat ease.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:48.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no sign of evil\nhere anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:52.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}In fact, the air is clean\nand clear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:55.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it because of Mt. Hakurei?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:03:00.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The spiritual mountain that purges the\nsins of all criminals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:09.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard of a place where even villains like\nme can find salvation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:14.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please take this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:17.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}... this lock of my hair to that place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:25.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me... but I will not be able\nto fulfill your wish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.91,0:03:30.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To live is to die.\NTo die is to live...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:41.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:48.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:53.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:59.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You protected everyone from\nthe heat of the flames with your fox fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But everyone stopped breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:18.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:23.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Open your eyes, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:26.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say something! Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not shake her like that, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:31.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:35.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Both you and Shippo will end\nup burning to death, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:38.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must escape to\na safer place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:02.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:10.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only I had been more suspicious\nof Renkotsu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:14.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only I had beaten\NGinkotsu much sooner!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:17.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:18.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:20.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:24.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If they all die, everything I did\nwas for naught!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If only I hadn't brought\nthem to this temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:31.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:33.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all because of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Enough of your crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:42.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Crying will solve nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:44.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must take these three\nto an open area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:53.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't force yourself, Shippo.\NI'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:56.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:06.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stay alive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:11.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:15.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure we'll find\NKagome here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:17.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that mutt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:23.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I doubt it, but what if he couldn't\nprotect Kagome?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:32.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That girl died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:41.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Why these tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't feel sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:57.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Shippo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:03.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you positive that the three\nof them swallowed the antidote?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh... yeah. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:10.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was a special antidote\nthat Jinenji gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:15.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yet... it had no effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:17.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, where did Inuyasha go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That he's gone to\ntake revenge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:33.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,C'mon out, Band of Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:35.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:37.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you wanna fight,\nc'mon out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:39.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jakotsu! Renkotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you others!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:44.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill every\none of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:49.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit hiding and come out\nto fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So Renkotsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:05.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:07.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:09.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I had my mind on Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:15.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So when I was fighting that Koga,\NI couldn't really get into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you let him get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:24.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's unlike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:26.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The guy ran super fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:31.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:36.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right. This is just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:45.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just wait, Ginkotsu.\NYou will be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:47.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:51.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall make you much,\nmuch stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:10.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder what Inuyasha's\ndoing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I messed up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:21.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I had seen through\NRenkotsu's true self...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:24.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:26.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you cursing\nyourself over, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:31.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm in no mood\nto talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:36.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... Only now you realize\nhow weak you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:38.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:41.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, you're only a half-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:45.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can barely take\ncare of yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:49.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and yet you wield the Tetsusaiga\nwhich was forged to protect others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was impossible from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:56.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then maybe I should kill you\nand take your Tenseiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:59.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I can resurrect Kagome\nand the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:03.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph! As if you can master\nmy Tenseiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Won't know unless I try!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:16.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:21.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is what I've done...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:25.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}making me see illusions\nof that bastard?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ready or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:29.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?\NHe's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, there's Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:36.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!\NWhere have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:38.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Found him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:39.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:41.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:43.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Found who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:45.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:48.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:53.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brat? Oh, you mean the boy\nwho was with Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:54.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Kohaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:11:00.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! Just a minute, Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:04.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Sesshomaru going to\nkill Kohaku, after all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:10.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo, don't cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Men never show their tears,\nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:21.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:24.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:27.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me! Forgive me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:30.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just because I'm so hopeless...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:34.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You... you had to go through this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:36.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:39.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't... breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:42.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm {\i1}dizzy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:50.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:55.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sucked out a lot of blood\nwith the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:56.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:03.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even for me, this poison\nis pretty potent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:06.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga... you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:12.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... you'll bear my child?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:13.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shoulda let this one die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:17.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:21.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, was it just a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How disappointing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:26.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was dreaming about\na woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:36.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone... is... alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:39.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was able to revive you because
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:43.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the poison had not completely\ngone through your system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:47.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I made it in the knick of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:49.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we've gotta hand it\nto you, Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:52.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess you can be\nuseful sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:55.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Insolence! I'm always useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:13:01.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Inuyasha...\nfor making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:03.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid!\NWhy apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:13.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:20.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with you, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:23.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You told me not\nto cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:24.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:25.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:27.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be silly, Shippo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have served Inuyasha for\nmany, many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I have never once\nseen him shed tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not lying... look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:37.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:40.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why should I cry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:47.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha... thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:50.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pure is impure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:53.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impure is pure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:55.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good is bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:57.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bad is good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To live is to die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:03.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}To die is to live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:07.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps it is the power of\NMt. Hakurei to purge...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:11.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in the surrounding areas,\nthere is absolutely no miasma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Almost too pure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:21.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It must be painful\nfor you, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:29.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it impossible to try to\nget any closer to Mt. Hakurei?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:47.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sense the presence of\na Sacred Jewel shard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:56.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:57.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come again in three days\nand I shall apply more ointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:04.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:05.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That man...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has a Sacred Jewel shard\nin his neck.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:14.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You take care, too, Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh my! Such a beautiful Priestess!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:25.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, that is Doctor Suikotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:26.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chiyo... do we have a visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:34.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are known as Suikotsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My name is Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:39.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:45.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whether it be a demon or human...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:49.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}if one with a wicked heart implants\na Sacred Jewel shard in the body,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:52.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the shard will become\ntotally defiled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:58.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}However... this man's shard\nis not tarnished at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not only that, this man...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}is one who is already dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Inuyasha, that I let\nthe Sacred Jewel shard get stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:20.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:22.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can always get it\nback later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:25.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But hey, drink this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:28.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku... Sango!\NBoth of you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is... it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:32.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just drink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's my special potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sucked out a large amount of\nblood from you three
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:38.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,along with the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:40.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now if you drink that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it'll increase your blood\nand make you healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:48.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even then... this is pretty\nhard to swallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:53.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just grin and bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:55.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With all of us in a weakened state,\nand needing care,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha can't make his move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:02.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's right.\NWe have to get better quickly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:06.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Myoga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:08.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I brought more ingredients!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:09.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:12.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:17.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I regurgitate the blood of\nthis poison snake with herbs,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,my special, secret potion\nwill be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:21.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Churn, churn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:26.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:27.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:34.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:36.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...starting to\nfeel more sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It would've been tolerable\nif we didn't know how it was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:46.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:47.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm glad! You're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:51.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:54.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:56.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey mutt, you're alive, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:58.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:05.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I was pursuing Naraku
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:07.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,when a strange fellow\nwielding a snake-like sword appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could that have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:11.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Jakotsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:14.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And he said that Kagome\nwas dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:17.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You came because\nyou were worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Holding her hands like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:21.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll really kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:23.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut your big trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:24.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:27.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome's hands are much\ncolder than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:30.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And her cheeks which are\nusually so rosy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,are pale like a fish's belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:36.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll bet you put Kagome's life\nin terrible danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:41.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I'd never let anything\nlike that happen! Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:43.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you... - !
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:46.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:48.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:49.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't take it either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Teach 'im a lesson!\N- Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:53.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:54.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.97,0:19:00.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll... I'll never put Kagome\nin such a situation again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:02.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you can get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:05.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:06.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:08.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:16.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These children lost their parents\nto famine and disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:20.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And so... I've been taking\ncare of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:23.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're sleeping so soundly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:28.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:30.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.74,0:19:33.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:35.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something terrible's happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:39.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu!\NPlease help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:40.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:44.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He fell and cut his leg\nwith a sickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It hurts! Hurts so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:47.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:53.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is there anything I can do\nto help?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:55.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:20:00.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NYou're so pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:03.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:07.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:10.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The wound is not as\ndeep as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:11.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:15.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're perspiring profusely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:21.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall I take over?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:25.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you...\NPlease do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:32.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:33.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:35.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:39.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:42.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu doesn't\nlike the sight of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:46.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I call myself a physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:50.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The moment I see blood,\nmy whole body starts to shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:54.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've been a doctor in this village\nthroughout your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:55.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:56.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was born in the eastern region.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:21:00.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I traveled to many villages\nministering to patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And finally ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:06.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a wonderful village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:09.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's poor, but because it's deep\nin the cold north,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the war hasn't reached us\nand it's peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:12.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:21.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:23.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:25.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:34.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:35.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must wash my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:37.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must wash...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.93,0:21:39.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I must wash...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.37,0:21:42.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no blood on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:46.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu gets like\nthat sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:47.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When it's bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:50.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he'll keep washing for\nan hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:53.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It won't come off.\NIt won't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:56.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It still won't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:49.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Another dead person appears\nwith a Sacred Jewel shard in possession!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:50.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You belong to the Band of Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:52.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am a physician, Suikotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:54.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're mistaking me\nfor someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.30,0:23:57.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit lying and show your\ntrue self!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.34,0:23:59.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chiyo, Yuta... run away!
